<figureCitation id="13322A0992417723FC04FA26FB10BA5B" box="[1018,1153,1526,1552]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="15.[136,229,1198,1220]" captionTargetBox="[358,1229,190,1173]" captionTargetId="figure-19@15.[358,1229,190,1173]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 10. Specimens in vivo. A. Bertolonia igrapiuna. B. B. linearifolia. C. B. reginatoi. D. B. violacea. E. B. vitoriana. F. Bertolonia sp, belonging to the B. maculata/B. marmorata species complex. Photos:A, C and D by L. F. Bacci; B by F. Michelangeli; E and F by A. M. A. Amorim." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6597710" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6597710/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="170">Figures 10b</figureCitation>
